{"tid":1257532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家可唔可以一齊贏返一次","createTime":"2019-06-25T15:11:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T17:38:58.000Z","uid":44493,"like":58,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7445697f00ecd542445d647c7da061ea66af48d2","tid":1257532,"uid":44493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T15:11:03.000Z","msg":"頭先我由屯門返屋企，行過大會堂果邊<br />\n見到有兩個青年派單張，叫人聽日出黎領事館巡遊<br />\n行到屯門西鐵站，又見到有人呼籲查黑警<br />\n返到屋企附近，又見到三個後生仔講五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n返到屋企坐低，我係度諗<br />\n究竟我仲可以做d 咩野？<br />\n幾時開始我變到咁冇用，居然要由廿歲都未到嘅細路黎守護我嘅將來<br />\n<br />\n明明5年前發夢出金鐘果個係我，果日一行出地鐵站<br />\n果種感覺我呢一世都唔會忘記，因為果一刻我以為自己去左戰場，隨時都會死<br />\n到今日除左69，616我出過黎，同身邊人解釋發生緊咩事，捐少少錢眾籌登報<br />\n我仲做過d 乜？<br />\n<br />\n屋企隻化骨龍明明仲玩緊玩具，突然間爬過黎扭計要抱<br />\n我扭起佢，望住佢對眼，我忍唔住喊左出黎<br />\n我好想為個衰仔，為香港做返少少野<br />\n我好想香港人一齊贏返一次<br />\n一次都好<br />\n<br />\n聽日<br />\n朝早有去領事館巡遊表達訴求<br />\n夜晚有愛丁堡廣場嘅集會<br />\n各位有時間嘅希望大家會出黎<br />\n淨係朝早又好，淨係夜晚又好<br />\n真係忙嘅，搵5分鐘推下post，share 俾身邊人知<br />\n希望大家唔好話其他人唔出黎/唔推post/唔課金眾籌等等<br />\n每個人都有自己困難/長處，總之大家盡能力做好自己果份<br />\n大家分工合作，威返一次俾全世界人睇<br />\n<br />\n多謝各位睇到呢度<br />\n講到1999，唔好意思"},{"pid":"3c20c415611c26a9559f2a61b905e271e32bfed5","tid":1257532,"uid":197540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T15:11:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1528bec28a4faef2c9962c3520c62eef7970fc86","tid":1257532,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T15:12:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c061a9a842450192af9920888f6413b4cad7821","tid":1257532,"uid":167277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T15:12:42.000Z","msg":"係, 大家爭氣d!!<br />\n唔可以放棄!! 要對得住所有義士同烈士!!"},{"pid":"5da4dff32e92d90798e54693fc8bfa2d21708651","tid":1257532,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T15:13:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"603695fdfe36d5bdfc8f27215ff3e068f474874a","tid":1257532,"uid":33833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T15:13:17.000Z","msg":"講得好 聽日見"},{"pid":"2a0f00027b8e2f0bdee5bd2cce4a5dbb380e6672","tid":1257532,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T15:13:48.000Z","msg":"你係香港嘅一份子，冇人會怪你<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eb78482108da69876c01964584363b5801d9480","tid":1257532,"uid":44493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"603695fdfe36d5bdfc8f27215ff3e068f474874a","tid":1257532,"uid":33833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T15:13:17.000Z","msg":"講得好 聽日見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T15:43:05.000Z","msg":"聽日見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01842bfcedcafac76bad095bb6a2d573a5d50889","tid":1257532,"uid":150083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T15:44:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c3becd58a9b30090e443cd33e137dcc4ac62139d","tid":1257532,"uid":218731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T15:45:00.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"9df5a6b78d2bf0809e172c8bc0370c5e82ea504d","tid":1257532,"uid":44493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a0f00027b8e2f0bdee5bd2cce4a5dbb380e6672","tid":1257532,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T15:13:48.000Z","msg":"你係香港嘅一份子，冇人會怪你<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T15:45:06.000Z","msg":"我寧願大家怪我，但係大家都會願意行多一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj